"construct the object by selecting the start and end point somewhere in the "
"&kig; window."
msgstr ""
"Vali <menuchoice><guimenu>Objektid</guimenu><guisubmenu>Vektorid ja lõigud</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Vektor</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ning loo objekt, "
"valides kuskil &kig;i aknas algus- ja lõpp-punkti."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:455
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To adjust length and direction of the vector you have to edit its start "
